{"prompt": "Develop a site for an independent film production company. The visuals should be artistic and include a deep yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Luminance Films</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #e6cc00; /* Deep Yellow */\n            --secondary-color: #333300; /* Darker, muted yellow/brown for contrast */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a00; /* Very dark, almost black yellow */\n            --accent-color: #ffff99; /* Lighter yellow for highlights */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--secondary-color), var(--primary-color));\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 20px 0 0 0;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            background: url('data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1440 320\"><path fill=\"%23e6cc00\" fill-opacity=\"1\" d=\"M0,224L48,224C96,224,192,224,288,192C384,160,480,96,576,96C672,96,768,160,864,192C960,224,1056,224,1152,192C1248,160,1344,96,1392,64L1440,32L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z\"></path></svg>') no-repeat bottom;\n            background-size: cover;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .content {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .content h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .film-gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .film-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .film-item::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0), rgba(0,0,0,0.7));\n            pointer-events: none;\n        }\n\n        .film-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .film-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .film-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .film-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-info {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info a:hover {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Luminance Films</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#films\">Films</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Capturing Stories in Light and Shadow</h2>\n            <p>Independent cinema that sparks imagination and ignites conversation.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>About Us</h3>\n            <p>Luminance Films is a passionate collective of storytellers dedicated to creating authentic and visually compelling cinema. We believe in the power of independent film to explore diverse perspectives and push creative boundaries.</p>\n            <p>From concept to final cut, we pour our hearts into every project, crafting narratives that resonate long after the credits roll.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"films\" class=\"content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Films</h3>\n            <div class=\"film-gallery\">\n                <div class=\"film-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e6cc00/1a1a00?text=Film+Poster+1\" alt=\"Film Poster 1\">\n                    <h4>Whispers in the Dust</h4>\n                    <p>A haunting drama exploring memory and loss in a desolate landscape.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"film-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e6cc00/1a1a00?text=Film+Poster+2\" alt=\"Film Poster 2\">\n                    <h4>The Gilded Cage</h4>\n                    <p>A visually stunning period piece about societal expectations and hidden desires.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"film-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e6cc00/1a1a00?text=Film+Poster+3\" alt=\"Film Poster 3\">\n                    <h4>Echoes of Tomorrow</h4>\n                    <p>A thought-provoking sci-fi narrative questioning the nature of reality.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Luminance Films. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p>Contact us: <a href=\"mailto:info@luminancefilms.com\">info@luminancefilms.com</a></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}